    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>19th-century women's bonnets, often with a soft gathered crown and a stiff brim with ribbons tied at the side or under the chin.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
